===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[connoisseur]] in eating and drinking, someone who takes their [[food]] considerably more seriously than most.

====Usage notes====
'''Gourmet''' emphasizes interest in quality of food and enjoyment of eating, sometimes to an obsessive degree: someone who “lives to eat rather than eating to live”. By contrast, a {{term|gourmand|lang=en}} is someone more interested in quantity of food than quality.

